    "the extension is %@" : {
      "comment" : "Rule card when-fragment; list like .zip, .dmg."
    },
    "The fallback folder when no routine's path matches. Add routines for Desktop, Dropbox, or anything else fussy. Loose folders are ordinary directories at the top of the watch folder — Binky can move them as one piece without sorting inside. That skips built-in destinations (Images, Documents, etc.) and sends app bundles to Apps." : {
      "comment" : "Default folder section footer."
